IntSquare

IntSquare(char file,
          int rank)
Creates an IntSquare based on file and rank.

Parameters:
file - intended file for the square (as a letter)
rank - intended rank for the square
Ensures:
this.file() = Character.toLowerCase(file) - 'a' + 1, this.rank() = rank
Requires:
new IntSquareFactory().isSquare(Character.toLowerCase(file) - 'a' + 1, rank);

IntSquare

IntSquare(java.lang.String pos)
Creates an IntSquare based on a string representation of the tile position.

Parameters:
pos - string containing tile position
Ensures:
this.file() = Character.toLowerCase(pos.charAt(0)) - 'a' + 1, this.rank() = Integer.parseInt(pos.substring(1))
Requires:
new IntSquareFactory().isSquare( Character.toUpperCase(pos.charAt(0)) - 'a' + 1, Integer.parseInt(pos.substring(1)) );
